6Ô∏è‚É£ Data Sources (Clearly Stated)
No real customer or bank data is used.
1. Synthetic Bank Statements


Bank statement templates created programmatically


Genuine documents generated automatically


Tampered versions created by:


Editing amounts


Modifying text


Changing fonts


Recompressing selected regions





2. Public Sample Statements


Dummy/sample bank statement formats from public sources


Masked PDFs without personal data



Dataset Size Goal


~200 genuine statements


~600 manipulated versions


~800 total documents



